| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0332 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f986d2a1-2ae1-532d-8ee7-60a999e5b9a9"
